revision.text:
''Takeuioki no mikoto'' is a descendant of Watatsumi. See the family tree below for more info.

==Genealogy==
{{User:Immanuelle/Generations of Watatsumi}}

'''Takeuioki no mikoto''' is a grandson of [[Watatsumi]], son of {{ill|Furutama|ja|布留多摩命|en|draft:Furutama-no-mikoto|simple|User:Immanuelle/Furutama|fr|Furutama|lt=Furutama-no-mikoto|complete=true}}
__NOINDEX__
==Genealogy== {{User:Immanuelle/Generations of Watatsumi}} ==Footnotes== ===Notes=== <references group="lower-alpha"/> ===References=== [[Category:Original pages]] [[Category:original pages]][[Category:original pages]] [[ja:武位起命]][[category:original pages]][[Category:Is a descendant of Watatsumi.]] <!-- Takeuioki no mikoto. https://shinto.miraheze.org/wiki/Special:EditPage/Template:Generations_of_Watatsumi {{ill|Takeuioki no mikoto|...|ja|JAPANESE|...}} ==Output Template== Output should take a form like the following '''{{ill|Takeuioki no mikoto|...|ja|JAPANESE|...}}''' (JAPANESE__NOINDEX__} is a descendant of Watatsumi. __NOINDEX__ [[Category:Original pages]] [[Category:original pages]][[Category:original pages]] [[Category:is a descendant of Watatsumi. --> [[ja:武位起命]][[category:original pages]][[Category:Is a descendant of Watatsumi.]] ]]

