'''Takeuioki no mikoto''' (武位起命) is a grandson of [[Watatsumi]], son of {{ill|Furutama|ja|布留多摩命|en|draft:Furutama-no-mikoto|simple|User:Immanuelle/Furutama|fr|Furutama|lt=Furutama-no-mikoto|complete=true|12=draft|12=draft}}} and father of {{ill|Saonetsuhiko|fr||ja|椎根津彦|simple|User:Immanuelle/Saonetsuhiko|lt=Saonetsuhiko|lt2=珍彦命|complete=true|12=draft|12=draft}}<ref name="Saonetsuhiko" /><ref name="gov" /><ref name="hyakka">{{ill|Matoshi Suzuki|ja|鈴木眞年|12=draft|12=draft}} {{nihongo|Hyakka Keizu Kou|百家系図稿}}</ref> He was also the father of {{ill|Yatamiko no mikoto|ja|八玉彦命|12=draft|12=draft}}
